  <source>Shahid Beheshti University of Medical Sciences</source>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to determine whether Pulsed Dye Laser therapy are effective in
      the treatment of Cutaneous Dermatophytosis.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      This study was conducted to determine the efficacy of Pulse Dye Laser in skin fungal
      infection, if this study showed that Laser could be effective, this would be introduced as a
      new treatment modality.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
